---
/** Three identity layers — User, Patient profile, Health profile */
---

<figure class="client-flow-diagram client-flow-diagram--large" aria-labelledby="fulfillment-identity-title">
  <figcaption id="fulfillment-identity-title" class="client-flow-diagram__caption">
    Three layers — do not conflate User, patient profile, and health profile
  </figcaption>
  <svg viewBox="0 0 920 220" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" role="img">
    <defs>
      <marker id="fi-arrow" markerWidth="8" markerHeight="8" refX="6" refY="4" orient="auto">
        <path d="M0 0 L8 4 L0 8 Z" fill="#5E7C7B" />
      </marker>
    </defs>

    <rect x="80" y="24" width="220" height="88" rx="12" fill="#E6EDEC" stroke="#DED9CC" />
    <text x="190" y="54" text-anchor="middle" fill="#5E7C7B" font-family="Barlow, sans-serif" font-size="10" font-weight="700" letter-spacing="1.2">LAYER 1</text>
    <text x="190" y="78" text-anchor="middle" fill="#1F3A3D" font-family="Barlow, sans-serif" font-size="16" font-weight="700">User</text>
    <text x="190" y="98" text-anchor="middle" fill="#6E7A78" font-family="Barlow, sans-serif" font-size="11">OTP login · mobile · roles</text>

    <line x1="300" y1="68" x2="340" y2="68" stroke="#5E7C7B" stroke-width="2" marker-end="url(#fi-arrow)" />
    <text x="320" y="58" text-anchor="middle" fill="#6E7A78" font-family="Barlow, sans-serif" font-size="10">owns</text>

    <rect x="340" y="24" width="260" height="88" rx="12" fill="#1F3A3D" />
    <text x="470" y="54" text-anchor="middle" fill="#B87333" font-family="Barlow, sans-serif" font-size="10" font-weight="700" letter-spacing="1.2">LAYER 2 · PHASE 1</text>
    <text x="470" y="78" text-anchor="middle" fill="#F7F0DD" font-family="Barlow, sans-serif" font-size="16" font-weight="700">Patient profile</text>
    <text x="470" y="98" text-anchor="middle" fill="#F7F0DD" font-family="Barlow, sans-serif" font-size="11" opacity="0.85">UHID · demographics · consent</text>

    <line x1="600" y1="68" x2="640" y2="68" stroke="#5E7C7B" stroke-width="2" marker-end="url(#fi-arrow)" />
    <text x="620" y="58" text-anchor="middle" fill="#6E7A78" font-family="Barlow, sans-serif" font-size="10">later</text>

    <rect x="640" y="24" width="220" height="88" rx="12" fill="#FFFFFF" stroke="#C8613A" stroke-width="1.25" stroke-dasharray="5 4" />
    <text x="750" y="54" text-anchor="middle" fill="#C8613A" font-family="Barlow, sans-serif" font-size="10" font-weight="700" letter-spacing="1.2">LAYER 3 · LOOP 3</text>
    <text x="750" y="78" text-anchor="middle" fill="#1F3A3D" font-family="Barlow, sans-serif" font-size="16" font-weight="700">Health profile</text>
    <text x="750" y="98" text-anchor="middle" fill="#6E7A78" font-family="Barlow, sans-serif" font-size="11">Graph projection · not Phase 1</text>

    <rect x="16" y="140" width="888" height="56" rx="10" fill="#F7F0DD" stroke="#DED9CC" />
    <text x="460" y="164" text-anchor="middle" fill="#1F3A3D" font-family="Barlow, sans-serif" font-size="11" font-weight="600">Every diagnostic order and Zen report belongs to the patient profile — not to a bare User</text>
    <text x="460" y="182" text-anchor="middle" fill="#6E7A78" font-family="Barlow, sans-serif" font-size="10">Do not build or promise the patient-facing health profile during Loop 1 Fulfillment</text>
  </svg>
</figure>
